[node name="Instructions" type="RichTextLabel" parent="CanvasLayer/UI/HowToPlayPanel/ContentCenter/InstructionsContainer"]
layout_mode = 2
size_flags_vertical = 3
bbcode_enabled = true
theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 26
text = "[b]Goal:[/b]
Move chess pieces to create lines of 5+ matching pieces to clear them and score points.

[b]Movement:[/b]
- Click a piece to select it
- Valid move cells are highlighted yellow
- Click a highlighted cell to move
- Pieces can only move to empty cells
- Each piece type moves differently (chess rules)

[b]Clearing Lines:[/b]
Lines are removed when they have 5+ aligned pieces:

[color=RED]• Color Line:[/color] 5+ pieces of the same color → normal score
[color=GREEN]• Type Line:[/color] 5+ pieces of the same type → double score
[color=YELLOW]• Combo:[/color] Same color AND type → combo bonus

[b]Scoring:[/b]
- Color line: 100 pts per piece
- Type line: 200 pts per piece
- Longer lines = bonus multiplier

[b]Pieces:[/b]
[color=LIME]Pawn[/color]: Moves forward (away from its color border), attacks diagonally
[color=AQUA]Knight[/color]: L-shaped jumps
[color=PURPLE]Bishop[/color]: Diagonal slides
[color=ORANGE]Rook[/color]: Horizontal/vertical slides
[color=PINK]Queen[/color]: Any direction slides
[color=GRAY]King[/color]: One step any direction (rare piece)

Press [b]ESC[/b] or click [b]Back[/b] to return"

[node name="HSeparator2" type="HSeparator" parent="CanvasLayer/UI/HowToPlayPanel/ContentCenter/InstructionsContainer"]
